reviewText: Playboy Video Centerfold: Morgan Fox Miss World Canada is 43 minutes long and was released on video in 1991. This video is in two parts. Morgan Fox is in the first part for twenty-three minutes and she is sexy and beautiful. With the exception of the intro, rap, and movie segments she is totally nude. Morgan Fox is Playboy Playmate of the Month for December 1990 and Miss World Canada in 1988. In part two we get a Playmate Bonus, Wendy Kaye. Wendy is Playboy Playmate of the Month for July 1991. Wendy is basically nude in and out of the seventeen minutes that are dedicated to her. Wendy is nude about 60% of the time. Both Playmates are beautiful in their birthday suits. Playboy Video Centerfold: Morgan Fox Miss World Canada gets a B+.
